You should get ready Installing chef and knife-solo by RubyGems

$mkdir -f ~/vagrant/centos
$cd ~/vagrant/centos
$vagrant box add centos http://developer.nrel.gov/downloads/vagrant-boxes/CentOS-6.4-x86_64-v20130427.box # Download VM Image
$vagrant init # make Vagrantfile (= a Vagrant setting file)

$emacs Vagrantfile
config.vm.box = "base"
â†“
config.vm.box = "centos"

$vagrant up # boot VM
$knife cook prepare centos # Install Chef and so on In VM
$vagrant ssh-config --host centos >> ~/.ssh/config # Setting up Local ssh

How to Login
1. $vagrant ssh
or
2. $ssh centos
